txt.en: 'Our stable is ready for horses to come and fill it. There are many horses out there upon the plains which have been trained and groomed for a variety of tasks and jobs. Each area of the Eastemnet has their own section of expertise. We should bring in horses trained by each of these areas.'
'Hytbold is one step closer to being rebuilt and restored.'
There is much work to do to rebuild the town of Hytbold.
